Class Description
AppState
Class representing current state of application.
Controller
Manages setup of GUI components, primarily their action handlers.
CustomHTMLEditor
Custom extension of HTMLEditor that enables adding images and saving of content.
ElementType
A class used to distinguish between files (notes) and directories (groups)
FileTree
Class to represent journal structure.
Helpers
Set of static methods used in application that don't quite fit anywhere.
LoadTreeVisitor
Implementation of SimpleFileVisitor used to load journal files and directories into a FileTree.
Main
Application entry point class.
